&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;D&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ur&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is unlikely that individuals entering this apprenticeship without previous experience will complete the apprenticeship in less than&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;36 months, and a typical completion time is likely to be 48 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;E&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;try Requirements and Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Individual employers will identify any relevant entry requirements in terms of previous qualifications, trainability tests, or other criteria. Most candidates will have English and Mathematics at level 2 on entry. For apprentices that have not, they must achieve level 2 English and maths within their apprenticeship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Level&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a level &lt;strong&gt;3 &lt;/strong&gt;Apprenticeship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Review date&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Apprenticeship standard will be reviewed in three years.&lt;/p&gt;
